      <title>俄罗斯暂时限制向美国运送核燃料</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/russia-temporarily-limits-enriched-uranium-supplies-to-us-m3ivvj3g</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯暂时限制向美国出口浓缩铀，这给运营美国反应堆的公用事业公司带来了潜在的供应风险，这些反应堆占美国电力供应的近五分之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/russia-temporarily-limits-enriched-uranium-supplies-to-us-m3ivvj3g</guid>
