    <item>
      <title>特朗普选择行业怀疑论者肯尼迪担任健康股总裁 导致健康股下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/health-stocks-slide-as-trump-picks-vaccine-skeptic-kennedy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普提名著名疫苗怀疑论者罗伯特·F·肯尼迪 (Robert F. Kennedy Jr.) 领导国家卫生和医学研究机构后，华尔街衡量了这位著名疫苗怀疑论者可能对该行业产生的影响，医疗类股因此暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/health-stocks-slide-as-trump-picks-vaccine-skeptic-kennedy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 11:11:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国股市已回吐大选后涨幅的一半</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/us-stocks-have-already-reversed-a-third-of-post-election-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着周五的抛售加剧，标准普尔 500 指数已回吐了选举后涨幅的一半以上，通胀坚挺和美联储的鹰派言论打压了市场人气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/us-stocks-have-already-reversed-a-third-of-post-election-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 09:31:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：美联储降息预期成焦点，股市进一步下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于特朗普交易失去动力且投资者押注美联储将不得不放慢政策宽松步伐，股市下跌，标准普尔 500 指数创下两个多月以来最糟糕的一周。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 22:20:41 GMT</pubDate>
